t now how to snap, like me (#truefact).<\/p>\n<p>If given the option right now, would you accept it?\u00a0 Or are you already DOING what you love and making a generous amount of money at the same time?? You already know the answer I&#8217;d choose since I&#8217;ve <a href=\"https:\/\/budgetsaresexy.vercel.app\/2011\/10\/full-time-blogger-goal\/\">already chosen it<\/a>,\u00a0 and the funny thing there was that I actually DID take a <a href=\"https:\/\/budgetsaresexy.vercel.app\/2011\/05\/is-a-dream-job-worth-it-if-you-cant-save-any-money\/\">50% pay cut<\/a>! Haha&#8230; so perhaps this is one of those &#8220;life mimicking art&#8221; type deals? ;)<\/p>\n<p><strong>Regardless, we&#8217;re here to talk about YOU today.\u00a0 <\/strong>And all your dreams and financial flexibility.\u00a0 If give the option to start your own dream job tomorrow for half the pay, would you jump on it? And what would that job\/dream be?<\/p>\n<p>&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;<br \/>\n<em>(Photo by <a href=\"http:\/\/www.flickr.com\/photos\/diggingforfire\/\">Digging For Fire<\/a>)<\/em><\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>It&#8217;s time for another rousing game of Would Your Rather!\u00a0 Y&#8217;all did so good spewing your thoughts on the last one between fame or fortune,&#8230; <\/p>\n<p class=\"more\"><a class=\"more-link\" href=\"https:\/\/budgetsaresexy.vercel.app\/would-you-rather-money-vs-dream-job\/\">Read More<\/a><\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":3,"featured_media":43124,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"footnotes":""},"categories":[45,88],"tags":[],"class_list":["post-24129","post","type-post","status-publish","format-standard","has-post-thumbnail","hentry","category-career","category-would-you-rather"],"yoast_head":"<!-- This site is optimized with the Yoast SEO Premium plugin v24.6 (Yoast SEO v24.5) - https:\/\/yoast.com\/wordpress\/plugins\/seo\/ -->\n<title>Would You Rather... Money vs